		tag: 10 bits
		conf: 5 bits
		retired_value: 64 bits
		stride: 64 bits
		instance ctr: 7 bits
		bits/SVP entry: 150 bits
	Total storage cost (bits) = 1024 (150 SVP entries x 153600 bits/SVP entry) = 153600 bits
